## NuFIT v5.2 (2022) 1D Δχ² Profiles

This directory contains the one-dimensional Δχ² profile data from the NuFIT 5.2 (2022) release for Normal Ordering (NO).

Each parameter is provided as a two-column CSV file with:
- `x`: parameter value
- `dchi2`: Δχ² value

**Notes:**
- δ<sub>CP</sub> values have been converted to degrees (°)
- All Δχ² profiles have been shifted so that the minimum equals zero
